{"tid":1362471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「出老解」唔係要黎嚇連登仔，係嚇港豬","createTime":"2019-07-25T01:26:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T01:40:00.000Z","uid":267881,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6420f5141e4c22fd409e64b2751383abab0d5b03","tid":1362471,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:26:39.000Z","msg":"佢意思係：<br />\n<br />\n「嗱，你班香港人（權貴），再唔管好你班細路，我就唯有幫你地教仔架喇，出兵會破壞經濟，到時連你地都會重創，但係為左維護國家主權，我地不惜任何代價。」<br />\n<br />\n大部分港豬真係信到十足架，有名你叫港豬，其實最驚老解嘅係港豬，因為會令佢地利益受損。<br />\n<br />\n最近我周圍訪問淺藍港豬，得出以下結論：<br />\n「我地鬥唔過共產黨」<br />\n「祖國唔幫香港死得」<br />\n「我交咁多稅，唔好搞亂香港」<br />\n<br />\n深黃嘅你地緊係覺得佢地好幼稚好可笑<br />\n但好易就中左同溫層陷阱<br />\n如果你地每次都無視呢D論調，或者鬥惡<br />\n淺藍係永遠唔會染黃<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但其實唔難</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地需要更多支持<br />\n方法只有一個</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣</span><br />\n<br />\n「支國面臨改革開放以來最大債務危機，之前十幾年假大空充大頭鬼製造高增長假象，終於要面臨審判日，佢地唔會夠錢還，所以要用盡辦法揸乾香港人錢，佢地唔會坦白佢地嘅嘅邪惡陰謀，所以調返轉話香港要靠佢地，佢地會幫香港。」<br />\n<br />\n呢個道理，好多人信奉，但同時好多港豬唔知<br />\n支國債務十年黎升左幾多？<br />\n佔全球比例升左幾多？<br />\n佢地用咩方法填債？<br />\n我問班淺藍港豬，冇一個識答<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重點係信嘅人點樣將信息傳遞俾港豬</span><br />\n<br />\n素材唔使自己砌，識用google就任抄<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/tag/739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Ftag%2F739&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=968c9c6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/tag/739</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/lazybusiness/data/himnbob_103/1/1120/92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Flazybusiness%2Fdata%2Fhimnbob_103%2F1%2F1120%2F92.jpg&h=194b6091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180806/large/b0301a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180806%2Flarge%2Fb0301a.gif&h=dcc25d7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後點樣掠錢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1385000/1389025/big_white_elephant_inline_20160314_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1385000%2F1389025%2Fbig_white_elephant_inline_20160314_1024.jpg&h=4b1628b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上資訊需要整合簡化做圖<br />\n瘋狂貼連儂牆、大型遊行瘋狂派<br />\n<br />\n港豬面臨一個人生十字路口<br />\n信一班土匪，定係撐自己年青人<br />\n係時局迫佢地落注"},{"pid":"af9fca43a882d5aff7bc6dc817a7b070b536c870","tid":1362471,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:32:19.000Z","msg":"元朗手足有野講 727去唔去都入黎睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"54e69e4934dac81981531231a6804859171b1ff6","tid":1362471,"uid":279854,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:32:23.000Z","msg":"佢地活係中國好勁，美國好廢既平行世界<br />\n活係一個香港都是靠中國既平行世界<br />\n活係一個中國政權強大無比眾國俯首稱臣既平行世界<br />\n<br />\n佢地覺得中國對香港咁好點解要反抗<br />\n就算反抗都唔會贏，不如逆來順受<br />\n<br />\n所以只有揭穿中國強大既假面具<br />\n佢地先知驚<br />\n先知中國唔係世界既中心"},{"pid":"6622de7aa3a2ae6e5cbec000a52af36971a298d0","tid":1362471,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:35:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc3ed3e5ff29e32c47007353b8f8b782a5ac15ad","tid":1362471,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:37:32.000Z","msg":"係有道理嘅。。。<br />\n不過連登仔都應該鍾意攬炒多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a86dc1559492100e45c1b28fa07fb33a4288e0f","tid":1362471,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc3ed3e5ff29e32c47007353b8f8b782a5ac15ad","tid":1362471,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:37:32.000Z","msg":"係有道理嘅。。。<br />\n不過連登仔都應該鍾意攬炒多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\